Package: heuristicsmineR
Type: Package
Title: Discovery of Process Models with the Heuristics Miner
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Felix",
           family = "Mannhardt",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "felix.mannhardt@sintef.no")
Description: Discovery of process models (Causal nets) from 'bupaR' event logs based on the 
 Heuristics Miner algorithm. The discovered Causal nets can be visualised with frequency 
 and performance annotations.  
